headline: Boeing reports 44 commercial airplane deliveries in February
summary: In its commercial aircraft operations, Boeing (BA) reports 13 airplane gross orders and 44 commercial deliveries in February, according to data posted to its corporate website. Boeing reports 49 year-to-date gross orders, 41 year-to-date orders net of cancellations/conversions and 6,197 unfilled airplane orders as of February 28, 2025.
